{"tid":1668781,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"霸氣C朗：年齡只是一個數字","createTime":"2019-10-22T07:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T09:40:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5260ff425e7e9a78df0ba97623187f4b89decbed","tid":1668781,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】基斯坦奴朗拿度大可放下心頭大石了，因為萬人迷表明未盟掛靴的念頭，並揚言年齡，只是一個數字。<br />\n<br />\n即將於周二率領祖雲達斯出戰莫斯科火車頭的基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo），在賽前記者會上被問到掛靴的計劃時說：「年齡只是一個數字，這不代表34、35、36歲就是足球生涯結束。」<br />\n<br />\n「以我的表現、如何作賽、比賽方式、我仍自感良好、對球賽的想法，我都可展示日趨成熟。這帶來不同。」這位葡萄牙巨星早前表示享受足球以外的事，又謂不知一兩年後會發生甚麼事，一度引起無限揣測。」<br />\n<br />\n剛射入足球生涯第700球，又入選金球獎30人候選名單的C朗，揚言個人榮譽不比球隊重要，矢言要助祖雲達斯成為3冠王：「我們想贏意甲、意大利盃及歐聯，祖雲達斯該目光遠大，嘗試贏盡所有錦標。」<br />\n<br />\n祖記於D組兩戰得4分，與馬德里體育會同分，莫斯科火車頭及利華古遜分別得3分及0分。<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯VS莫斯科火車頭<br />\nNow TV 633及630台23/10 03:00直播<br />\nNow E 同步直播<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"ef0300f61ddd280f3d93bbaa81ce467cc40554bf","tid":1668781,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會踢到50歲"},{"pid":"c9448f33de7b5a210a7110ef223dcd3b440acdc4","tid":1668781,"uid":240613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"點解係牙朗放下心頭大石"},{"pid":"af7d2e94d4152d1b12d2bc6ca1dc17b4bb2a38e9","tid":1668781,"uid":41352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"係咪保方教佢講"},{"pid":"dfe769bb8149092b07434d427923f13cb56d1856","tid":1668781,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">快推行動po<br />\n推到有人搞</span></span><br />\n開咗兩個po都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線]  [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"882fa282c3a13057ed47613b9be02df952c7d986","tid":1668781,"uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"犯罪記錄都只是一個數字"},{"pid":"dda0755a2a79a477f22266c0e7ab39a9aa76ddc1","tid":1668781,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa55eaa88277545b7a5050cfc5c748f2a3a36ef","tid":1668781,"uid":4187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"咁屎眼係咩數字"},{"pid":"a3d11d6cbf4f6581be1e61a935318c8ef473da63","tid":1668781,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef0300f61ddd280f3d93bbaa81ce467cc40554bf","tid":1668781,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會踢到50歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"三蒲知良踢到60添<br />\n過到佢先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91bd38c5f00feecf06f0c1c5876db3a6bb5084f","tid":1668781,"uid":82389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"好想見到佢幫保方拎歐聯"},{"pid":"2789d1f6b713b14de23944110140cbe1aab1131b","tid":1668781,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"1000球 is coming"},{"pid":"18a05b88d2e62d507d1378f55ea2c84a5e3ddc02","tid":1668781,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:40:47.000Z","msg":"雞姦人就是犯罪！"}]}